title: My Cousin Vinny (1992) (Joe Pesci, Marisa Tomei)
description:
MY COUSIN VINNY - 1992

  Two carefree pals (Ralph Macchio and Mitchell Whitfield) 

traveling through Alabama are mistakenly arrested, and 

charged with murder. Fortunately, one of them has a 

cousin who's a lawyer - Vincent Gambini (Joe Pesci), a 

former auto mechanic from Brooklyn who just passed his 

bar exam after his sixth try. Vinny's never been in court - 

or in Alabama - and when he arrives with his leather-clad 

girlfriend (Marisa Tomei), to try his first case, it's a real 

shock - for him and the Deep South!

  Starring: Joe Pesci, Marisa Tomei, Ralph Macchio, 

Mitchell Whitfield, Fred Gwynne.

  Directed by: Jonathan Lynn.

  Quality: Very Good Xvid from DVD.

  Length: 1hr. 54min.

  Language: English.
